Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,阴阳师眼中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗 不知道你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,算不算是实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我…终于
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,加快速度 雪风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就可以了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,装甲鬼兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,无法接近祭坛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先降落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 我们往上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 你也该给我清醒清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,命是我的 我爱怎么用是我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会让哥哥复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不 根本就不应该去尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,灵魂之术之所以被严禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,究其原因是人类根本就不应该去涉足那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为那个咒法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是在人们对超越理解范围的东西心存敬畏的时代里炼成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在活在当世的人不可以鲁莽地去照猫画虎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以祭奠「泰山府君祭」的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,复活该仪式的都唯独你土御门一家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,难道只许州官放火不许百姓点灯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雪风 往下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 快停下 他们是打算前后夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这把剑真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是「护身剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,此剑可是经过特别锻造 而且是年代久远的灵剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是刚才那一下让刀刃缺了一角了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不过…不过就磕掉那么一丁点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在情况紧急 就算是弄折了也是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 你也来迎战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你居然不擅长实战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 祭祀仪式要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雪风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 北斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗?这是北斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 这条龙是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它是我的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,受历代当家驱使的使役式 是土御门家的守护圣兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.84,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}使役式：鬼神、灵兽等以灵体形式存在的古式式神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是为数不多的真龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你倒是早把它叫出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没法完全驾驭它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 这家伙没什么紧张感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗 我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去打倒敌人的式神!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快跳过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你别强人所难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 我听到了 你快放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我抱得死死的干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这把「护身剑」能用来攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把剑拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,南么 三曼多 勃驮喃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(498,660)}namah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}samanta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(762,660)}buddhanam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,印捺罗也 莎诃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(590,660)}indrah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(732,660)}svaha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:14.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注释:梵语，帝释天（梵名Sakra,Devanam-indra）真言。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,「护身剑」解封后 帝释天的力量就会消散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,变成「破敌剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 把那张弓给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,箭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是带咒力的桃木弓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,应该可以牵制敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 我来制造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,总之一定要阻止仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你可是我的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要听我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 结界解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又复活了?它要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它可不是一般厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 我们要去阻止仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太小瞧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咒符…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,弄不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多符咒全都是用自己的血写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,阴阳师 大连寺铃鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谨请泰山府君及冥界诸神…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目…这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…这种东西根本就不是神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,铃…鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,…还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,铃鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你制作了新的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够啊 铃鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等一下 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,会…给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的命…会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿就好 请再和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是杀死了北斗的仇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托…了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可…恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你这…臭小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,烧尽邪符 「急急如律令」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(735,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,给我住手 你这臭小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,灵脉?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这家伙 暗中作祟的就是它!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,混…蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 土御门家的血脉哟!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 您的心意依然不变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会永远等下去的 无论几度风雨沧桑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是你的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夜光大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,鍐 哞 怛落 纥里 恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(488,660)}vam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(545,660)}hu^m
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}tra^h
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(718,660)}hri^h
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(793,660)}ah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,五行连环 「急急如律令」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(733,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不能抬头看!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要看了一眼就会被摄走魂魄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雪风 已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快杀掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是为那个女人报仇还是什么别的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在说那种话之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是…先送你哥哥一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,已经结束了 北斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个式符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,难道能够修复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 已经完全失去灵气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是被春虎称为北斗的那位应该还健在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个式神是操作型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 通过作为「北斗」的「她」与春虎接触的施法者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还在哪里生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 是谁那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这个我想 春虎你应该比我更清楚才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我?我就连她是式神的事都不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还一直把你蒙在鼓里 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天还会再和她相见的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这次可真是闹得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 北斗那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像不怎么吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就觉得她是个奇怪的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 考虑到她靠近你的那个时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然对于她是谁的式神这一点我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,结果 至始至终都是谜一般的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,冬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢 想去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,式神必须随时待在主人身边才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,请尽快进入阴阳塾就读
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为土御门家的威望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还是因为铃鹿事件的功劳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 随便什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,能成为夏目的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呆虎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呆虎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,遭了 幻象?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也稍微…不晓得该如何下定决心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么用那种男人般的说话方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还有打扮也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是本家的「家规」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,「身为土御门家的继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在外言行举止须如男子」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,课是没有问题 应该说是「家规」那方面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那个时候说的是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 原因就是这样 所以你要配合我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再次请你多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了? 再次?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道真的全部明白了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 全部明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还一直把你蒙在鼓里 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太夸张了吧 又不是被你骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难道没有发现吗 刚才说「全部都明白了」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说 穿男装是「家规」这事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不明白 你这个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩个我真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,冬儿 事情已经办完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 只是去打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,之前和你提起的 我的青梅竹马夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么冬儿会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 为什么你会知道冬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 这家伙也一起进入阴阳塾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,进阴阳塾什么的 冬儿还是个外行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来就能「灵视」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,被卷入灵灾时的后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,原本就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擅长分辨人和式神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个发带很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 呆虎这称呼还真是很适合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个 在阴阳塾都是我的后辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给我作好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊 冬儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她平常不是那副模样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不…平时就一直都是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.83,0:23:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快点过来 呆虎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是是 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1147.17,322.5)\fs37.5\1c&H000000&\bord0}距离出场还有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056.604,450)\fs37.5\1c&H000000&\bord0}1集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,终于下周春虎大人要进阴阳塾了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,「咻」的插进去再转一转
